# Competitive teardown source allowlist

Copy this file to a run-specific `sources.md`, verify each source yourself, and
give scouts the filled path as `{{ALLOWLIST_PATH}}`.

Rules for the orchestrator:

- Add only URLs the scouts may cite.
- Keep one target per section.
- Prefer canonical pricing, docs, changelog, benchmark, terms, or product pages.
- Remove broad homepages unless the homepage itself is the source being compared.

## Target: ExampleCo

- https://example.com/pricing
- https://example.com/docs/rate-limits
- https://example.com/customers/example-case-study

## Target: SampleSuite

- https://samplesuite.example/pricing
- https://samplesuite.example/docs/api-limits
- https://samplesuite.example/blog/2026-product-benchmark
